<h1>Martijn Vermaat</h1>

<p>
This page intends to give at least a bit more information about me
than there is on <a href="./">my home page</a>.
<p>

<p>
I am <a href="http://www.cs.vu.nl/~mvermaat/">studying</a> Computer
Science (specialization
<a href="http://www.cs.vu.nl/~tcs/">Formal Methods &amp;
Software Verification</a>) at the VU University Amsterdam.
I also helped other students doing the same thing as a teaching
assistant for six years.
</p>

<p>
Currently, I am working on formalising infinitary rewriting in the Coq
proof assistant as part of my <a href="master-project">Master's thesis</a>.
</p>

<p>
Last.fm knows what music
I <a href="http://www.last.fm/user/mvermaat">listen to</a>.
</p>

